sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant AAW as «view»<br>:AdminApplicationsWindow
    participant AAC as «controller»<br>:AdminApplicationController
    participant VA as VolunteerApplication
    participant N as Notification

    note over Admin,N: USE CASE 1: VIEW VOLUNTEER APPLICATION
    Admin->>+AAW: request to view applications
    AAW->>+AAC: index(request)
    AAC->>+VA: retrieve applications list
    VA-->>-AAC: return application data
    
    opt view specific application
        AAC->>+VA: show(id)
        VA-->>-AAC: return application details
    end
    
    AAC-->>-AAW: return view with data
    AAW-->>-Admin: display volunteer applications

    note over Admin,N: USE CASE 2: MANAGE APPLICATION STATUS
    Admin->>+AAW: update status (e.g., Approve/Decline) & submit
    AAW->>+AAC: updateStatus(request, id)
    AAC->>+VA: update status in record
    VA-->>-AAC: status updated confirmed
    
    %% Send Notification automatically after status update
    AAC->>+N: notifyParticipant()
    N-->>-AAC: notification sent to participant
    
    AAC-->>-AAW: return success redirect
    AAW-->>-Admin: display updated status success message
